an absolute horror and abhorrence of war in general batzofin 
said 
fighting between guerrillas and security forces in namibia 
flared up again april 1 at the start of unsupervised transition 
period that is to end with territory becoming independent of south 
africa 
batzofin pleaded guilty and his attorneys asked the presiding 
magistrate to sentence him to community service rather than prison 
