hand the number of newspaper sales executives shes ever met 
advertisers perceive newspaper sales personnel as order 
takers dull not creative and just looking to sell 
space she said 
part of the problem is that young ad agency executives are 
products of the tv age they dont read newspapers as much they 
want exciting ad campaigns and they dont want to expend their 
energies on quarterpage newspaper ads 
she also pointed out that a majority of americans no longer get 
most of their news from newspapers 
advertisers she said are indifferent to pulitzer prizes 
newspapers need to target special segments of their audiences 
geographically and demograghically she said 
added value approaches such as joint promotions research 
crossmedia programs and merchandising are being used by magazines 
to protect their rate cards 
all of your major competitors are adapting to the requirement 
of mixed marketing it is time for you to do the same she said 
she said newspapers have the potential to launch a strong and 
unified strategy that could open up significant opportunities for 
sustained growth 
it also is time for editors to take more aggressive roles she 
said and convince advertising craftsman that newspapers are a 
hot visible medium 
while you cant take the show biz away from tv you can make 
newspapers more appealing by demonstrating the inroads made in 
areas like reproduction in fourcolor by making newspapers more 
profitable for agencies by standardizing contracts invoices rate 
structures and by being more flexible with new positioning and 
layout ideas she said 
she urged editors to support your ad sales efforts to entice 
new and repeat business with special incentives be innovative 
the church and the state must work together to ensure the 
preservation of the species that doesnt mean that anyones 
integrity must be compromised but in a fierce survival battle 
youve got to operate as a team and understand one anothers 
business the best way to protect your credibility and integrity is 
to secure a sound business future 
