limited partnership registered with the securities and exchange 
commission for an initial public offering with proceeds to be used 
to acquire and run plum creek 
plum creek has approximately 14 million acres of timberland and 
about 96 billion board feet of salable softwood timber in the 
pacific northwest it employs about 1800 people in washington 
idaho and montana and in 1988 had profits of 574 million on 
revenues of 3328 million 
