<TEXT>
belgian endive the butt of jokes during the 
presidential campaign is gaining respectability in massachusetts 
where researchers are developing new varieties and promoters call 
it the white gold of the vegetable kingdom 
more than 150 chefs and restaurant owners gathered thursday for 
a sumptuous repast of belgian endive with caviar cold cream of 
endive soup and braised endive with veal 
though he did not attend the toast of the 15000 party thrown 
by belgian produce shippers was gov michael s dukakis who 
appears to have nearly as devoted a following among endive sellers 
as among greekamericans 
hes certainly done a lot for us in publicity said franz 
dahlem director of the belgian endive marketing board and host of 
