the sale of their assets in bunker hunts case that 10 percent is 
estimated to be 15 million the brothers would also keep 
possession of their dallas homes and life interests in trusts 
left to them by their father hl hunt their other holdings would 
be liquidated and the proceeds split among about 4000 creditors 
each 
